&lt;li&gt;Work closely with VetAM, HSP, and Enterprise to ensure hospitals are matched with the right veterinary professionals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track hiring needs and placement opportunities to inform pipeline development.&lt;/li&gt;
