&lt;li&gt;Follow and uphold Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) developed by the senior manager and R2H squad.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify workflow gaps or bottlenecks and suggest process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
